OL,3,CSon of Aubrey Hames says his father
OL,4,Cnever got over wrongful corruption
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FNow his son Dominic has written a book
OL,8,Fabout his father's life and
OL,9,Fachievements which focuses on the
OL,10,Fcourt case and its subsequent impact.
OL,12,FDominic Hames says he wanted to put on
OL,13,Frecord that "not only was (his father)
OL,14,Finnocent, but he was unfairly charged
OL,15,Fand the case should never come up in
OL,16,Fthe first place".
OL,18,FWith his distinctive handlebar
OL,19,Fmoustache, Aubrey Hames had one of the
OL,20,Fhighest profiles of any council leader
OL,21,Fin Wales.
