OL,7,FAs a Labour councillor, he led the
OL,8,Fformer Newport Borough Council to
OL,9,Fwhich he had first been elected in
OL,10,F1954. He was mayor of Newport during
OL,11,Fthe jubilee year of 1977.
OL,13,FAnd he had played a prominent part in
OL,14,Fmany of the political battles of the
OL,15,Fperiod, including over the route of
OL,16,Fthe M4 and the building of the
OL,17,Frecently-demolished Newport Centre.
