OL,4,Cnever got over wrongful corruption
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FIn his full-time employment, he had
OL,8,Fbeen assistant docks manager at
OL,9,FCardiff from 1965 but his career came
OL,10,Fto an abrupt and difficult end when he
OL,11,Fwas sacked in 1977, at the exact same
OL,12,Ftime he was serving as Mayor of
OL,13,FNewport.
OL,15,FHe, along with a Cardiff businessman,
OL,16,Fwas accused of corrupt practices at
OL,17,Fthe docks.
