OL,3,CSon of Aubrey Hames says his father
OL,4,Cnever got over wrongful corruption
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FNow in his book, "Mr Newport," Dominic
OL,8,FHames has told his father's life story
OL,9,Fincluding the court case.
OL,11,FIn an interview with ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,12,Fhe explained the impact of what
OL,13,Fhappened on the family, saying: "We
OL,14,Fhad no real income after that. He
OL,15,F(Aubrey Hames) survived on his #10 a
OL,16,Fday allowance. He was in charge of the
OL,17,Fbiggest budget in Newport yet had the
OL,18,Flowest income."
