OL,3,CSon of Aubrey Hames says his father
OL,4,Cnever got over wrongful corruption
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"So 25 years after he died, people
OL,8,Fstill think there's no smoke without
OL,9,Ffire. So he just wanted it to be put
OL,10,Fdown in the record that not only was
OL,11,Fhe innocent, but that he was unfairly
OL,12,Fcharged and the case should never have
OL,13,Fcome up in the first place."
OL,15,FWhat happened may have cost Aubrey
OL,16,FHames his job and created stress and
OL,17,Fdistress for him and his family, but
OL,18,FDominic believes it led to his father
OL,19,Fmaking more of an impact on Newport.
