OL,3,CSon of Aubrey Hames says his father
OL,4,Cnever got over wrongful corruption
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"It probably made his political
OL,8,Fcareer," he said. "I don't think he
OL,9,Fwould have been the politician he
OL,10,Fbecame without it because he was, in
OL,11,Feffect, essentially Newport's first
OL,12,Ffull-time councillor, because he just
OL,13,Fthrew himself into his council work
OL,14,Fand he was at the Civic Centre all the
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,F"There's a lot of people out there who
OL,18,Fwill not be aware of his legacies, the
OL,19,Fproblems sorted out for their parents
OL,20,Fand grandparents.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
