OL,4,Cnever got over wrongful corruption
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"For instance, the residents of
OL,8,FBanewell (an area in central Newport);
OL,9,FBaneswell is old Victorian buildings
OL,10,Fnow rather than 1970s buildings
OL,11,Fbecause of Aubrey Hames.
OL,13,F"The route of the M4 would probably
OL,14,Fnow be going right through the middle
OL,15,Fof Newport. You think it's bad now, it
OL,16,Fcould have been far worse.
OL,18,F"And the Newport Centre was a nice
OL,19,Flegacy. No more (it's been demolished
OL,20,Fthis year) but Newport will be having
OL,21,Fa new leisure centre very soon.
